加夫尼的人称内战为"北方侵略战争"
In Gaffney, people called it the "War of Northern Aggression."

34
00:03:58,550 --> 00:04:00,850
个人而言  我并不以南部邦联为荣
I personally take no pride in the Confederacy.

35
00:04:01,070 --> 00:04:02,410
